<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="609" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="12.[1354,2561,723,1309]" pageId="12" pageNumber="609">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1356,1712,1117,1151]" pageId="12" pageNumber="609">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Recent separation from other similar taxa (
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="True" baseAuthorityYear="1892" box="[1866,2001,1160,1189]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Lophuromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="609" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="aquilus">L. aquilus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1906" box="[2020,2177,1160,1189]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Lophuromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="609" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="brunneus">L. brunneus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="W. Verheyen, Hulselmans, Dierckx &amp; E. Verheyen" authorityYear="2002" box="[2195,2312,1160,1189]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Lophuromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="609" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dudui">L. dudui</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="W. Verheyen, Hulselmans, Dierckx &amp; E. Verheyen" authorityYear="2002" box="[2330,2491,1160,1189]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Lophuromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="609" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="verhageni">L. verhageni</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dollman" authorityYear="1909" box="[1357,1451,1195,1229]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Lophuromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="609" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="zena">L. zena</taxonomicName>
) and subsequent distributional restriction of the Buff-spotted Brush-furred Rat to south-western Ethiopia make necessary a reassessment ofits conservation status.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
